title: Wild Week of Trading Leaves Pockmarks Across US Equity Landscape
description: Precious metals memed out, Bitcoin flamed out and the labor market looks like it’s petering out. None of it started in the equities market, but together it was enough — along with a reckoning for software firms — to shake the foundation of an AI-driven bull run.
